The preconfigured Sales Cloud dashboards and underlying reports are based on Sales Cloud objects and fields. Use these dashboards to track key performance metrics for your executives, sales managers, sales reps, and other team members.
REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Group (View Only), Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions
USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To install packages: Download AppExchange Packages
In AppExchange, search for Preconfigured Sales Cloud Dashboards.
Click Get It Now.
Install the package.
title: Installing and Using Salesforce Preconfigured Sales Cloud Dashboards
